-- ds.heading-medium: Align Content

`align-content` attribute aligns the content 
inside the `ds.column`. The default value is `align-content: center`.
You can choose other pre-defined 
align-content values like:

- top-left
- top-right
- top-center
- center
- bottom-left
- bottom-center
- bottom-right

